title: ArtyTorrent Pack 92-Electro Drum Loops 140-149bpm-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 92-Electro Drum Loops 140-149bpm-WAV
-----------------------------------------------------

A small pack of miscellaneous electro drum loops utilising the sounds of the TR-808 and 909. A few of these loops are in the 4/4 house style, but most are syncopated breaks.
Tempo ranges from 140-149 bpm.

Torrent contains 3 RAR files with 65 loops
------------------------------------------
Machine Lang El 140-149 (6 loops)
Misc Electro 140-149 (45)
Raft 140 (14)

Samples are from a variety of sources including CDs by EastWest, Sony/Sonic Foundry, and Loopology/Syntrillium, and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.

--
Arty - "Meet my friend Roland"
27th February 2008.
